{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01Ehn4onivXNvWMcLbL71JYN","type":"tool_result","content":"_bmad-output/planning-artifacts/epics-architecture-v3.md:507:### Story 15-4: Fix ~40 TS compilation errors in test files\n_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/epic-10-retrospective.md:98:**Action:** Epic 15 story `15-4-fix-ts-compilation-errors` exists in backlog. Should be prioritized.\n_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/session-retro-2026-03-25.md:98:- **Split `state.ts`** — Extract `generateSprintStatusYaml()` and related helpers into `src/modules/sprint/sprint-yaml.ts`. This has been deferred for 3+ sessions. Story 15-4 or a new TD story should cover it.\n_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/session-retro-2026-03-25.md:764:| 15-4-fix-ts-compilation-errors | **Not started** | Time budget exhausted |\n_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/session-retro-2026-03-25.md:819:- **Only 1 story completed** — Despite a backlog of 5 actionable stories (15-3 through 15-5 plus the 3 stuck verifiers), only 15-3 was completed. Time budget ran out before 15-4 and 15-5 could start.\n_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/session-retro-2026-03-25.md:834:- **Single-story sessions** — When infra blocks most stories, the remaining work gets stretched to fill the session. 15-3 didn't need 45 minutes; 15-4 could have started.\n_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/session-retro-2026-03-24.md:78:- **Pre-existing TS errors are accumulating.** ~10 test files have unrelated compilation issues. These create noise in every dev session and risk masking new errors. Story 15-4 exists for this but remains in backlog.\n_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/session-retro-2026-03-24.md:108:1. **Story 15-4: Fix pre-existing TS compilation errors** — 10 test files with unrelated errors. Growing noise.\n_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/session-retro-2026-03-24.md:188:- **Pre-existing TS errors reportedly jumped from ~10 to ~50.** Whether this is a real increase or